<style>
	.calendar-promo-content  li { margin:4px 8px;}
	.calendar-promo-content { margin:24px; font-size:12px; line-height:1.4em; }
</style>

<div class="calendar-promo-content">
	<div style="width:400px;height:207px;float:right;border:1px solid rgb(200,200,200);margin: 0 -65px 10px 10px">
		<img src="/images/calendar/promo_overview.png" width="100%">
	</div>
<h1>Staying organized just got easier</h1>
<p>Stixy helps you and your friends to organize all those projects that are continuously going on in your life. Now, by adding the Stixy calendar, getting organized by using Stixy got even easier.
<p>In addition to being able to enter events, set reminders, and so forth, the Stixy calendar gives you an overview of all your calendar widgets on your different Stixyboards, shared or not shared. This way, you can easily
keep track of your life both inside and outside of Stixy.

