	Your browser is not supported during this first phase of beta testing, but we expect to support it very soon.
	<p style="margin-top:8px"></p>
	If you like, we’d be happy to <%= link_to "notify you", { :controller => :calendar, :action => "beta_signup", :signup => true } %> when this happens.
